SEVERE THUNDERSTORM CAPABLE OF PRODUCING NICKEL SIZE HAIL...AND
DAMAGING WINDS IN EXCESS OF 60 MPH.  THIS STORM WAS LOCATED 9 MILES
NORTH OF MULLIN...OR ABOUT 15 MILES SOUTH OF COMANCHE...MOVING
NORTHEAST AT 35 MPH.

A TORNADO WATCH REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 100 AM CDT SATURDAY MORNING
FOR EASTERN TEXAS.

