WILL EXPIRE AT 8 PM.

RADAR INDICATED THAT HEAVY RAIN...SMALL HAIL...AND GUSTY WINDS WERE 
STILL POSSIBLE FROM THE THUNDERSTORM. A FLASH FLOOD WARNING REMAINS 
